Usage: delete_pg_keepout [-help] {-cell <string> | -inst <string> | -all } [-layer <string> | -layerId <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-all                      # remove all PG keepouts (bool, optional)
-cell <string>            # specify cell to remove PG keepout
                          # (string, optional)
-inst <string>            # specify inst to remove PG keepout
                          # (string, optional)
-layer <string>           # specify layers to remove PG keepout
                          # (string, optional)
-layerId <string>         # specify layer Ids to remove PG keepout
                          # (string, optional)